D&G; 10 La Roue De La Fortune EDT - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.3550

Dolce&Gabbana’s La Roue De La Fortune 10 lets her be herself as she floats on a creamy cloud of dreams. Don’t underestimate her; she is not frivolous and her feet remain firmly grounded. She is adventurous and creative yet demure - a dreamer if there was ever one. As she takes on the world at her own pace and sets her own standards this luxury aroma envelops her. The Eau de Toilette defines her in many ways the woman she was is and wants to be.

Peppy accords of pineapple and pink pepper take a strong hold of your senses before trailing into a heart note of jasmine gardenia and tuberose. The white flowers go straight to the head and leave you reeling under their mesmerising influence. The drama dies down gradually leaving you wrapped in the soft comforting bouquet of vanilla and patchouli which blend like butter with the mystical iris and languorous benzoin in the base notes of the fragrance.

The sparkly cool blue of La Roue De La Fortune 10 is caught up in Dolce&Gabbana’s Anthology range bottles which redefine simplicity. Learn who you are and what you stand for while wrapped in an aroma of perfection.
